'''Greg Ellis''' is an English screen and voice actor. He provided the voice for [[Mical]] in ''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords]]''. He also voices [[Turk Falso]] in ''[[Star Wars: The Clone Wars]]'' and [[Valen Rudor]] in ''[[Star Wars Rebels]]''.

{{Bio-stub}}

